::Scyther/EndBringer::

Scyther is thrown around by the wind, boosting off away from the 
battle as ordered. Behind him, EndBringer jumps over a few stray 
shots, finding a decendable path down the mountain and following it.




--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "CYBERWOLF4" <cyberwolf4@p...> wrote:
> Starscreams shots struck Megatons weaker T-Rex form. The mighty 
beast stumbled forward tripping and falling to the ground. he put one 
of his hands over a wound and wiped a red substance from his organic 
form. "What's this?" he wondered, smelling and tasteing it for the 
first time. "Plasma based substance with a slight scent of mech 
fluid, intrigueing." The great beast had thought Starscream was 
disabled, he now knew he had underestimated these bots, they were 
more sturdy than he had thought. He rised to his feat roaring his 
rage toward all on the battlefield. He stomped forward launching a 
blast of wind from  his lungs at Scyther and Inferno.
